Grade Chart
Visually see how your grade has changed over time, how each assignment affects your grade, how categories are broken down, and which new assignments have been put in.
Grade Calculator
GradeCompass's powerful Hypothetical Mode let you calculate what your grade would be if you got a score on an assignment, what you need to get on your final, and much more.
Attendance and more
GradeCompass breaks down your attendance by day and shows what periods you missed. It also shows your report cards, documents, and mail.
Private Login
GradeCompass does not have access to your data. When you use GradeCompass, your device connects directly to your student portal. We never see your password or your grades! Learn more
